== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior (Dragon Quest in Japan) features the Hero, a descendant of Erdrick, on a quest to defeat the Dragonlord and rescue Princess Gwaelin. This page documents the Hero's statistics and progression.

== Character Data Structure ==

Character data is stored in RAM at $00-$FF:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Address !! Size !! Description
|-
| $BC || 1 || Current HP
|-
| $BD || 1 || Max HP
|-
| $BE || 1 || Current MP
|-
| $BF || 1 || Max MP
|-
| $C0 || 1 || Strength
|-
| $C1 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $C5 || 1 || Level
|-
| $BA-$BB || 2 || Experience (little endian)
|-
| $BD-$BE || 2 || Gold (little endian)
|}

