== Combat Formulas ==

=== Attack Damage ===

<pre>
Damage = (Attack - Enemy_Defense/2) / 4 to (Attack - Enemy_Defense/2) / 2
</pre>

=== Spell Damage ===

<pre>
Hurt: 3-10 damage (random)
Hurtmore: 30-45 damage (random)
</pre>

=== Critical Hit ===

<pre>
Critical chance = (Hero_Level / 256) * 100%
Critical damage = undefended attack
</pre>

